      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "The one 'Mech we should have kept to make a fortune dismantling it and selling the <i>Dark Horse</i>'s parts as souvenirs to Banshee fans?\n\nI have by my bunk a picture of me sitting on the pilot's seat... that's one of my most valuable possessions right now.",
