    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7b3a98e93a397ebf56f879"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Wait, the one with the original [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTekBattleCom],Tek BattleCom]] electronics suite that [[DM.Factions[faction_AppleComputersInterstellar],Apple Computers Interstellar]] demanded back just because they claimed it to be stolen?\n\nI also remember it quite well... that piece of electronics was priceless [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLosTech],lostech]] even if it was pirated.",
      "branches": [
