      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c212d06bf9f6076cd69b8ee"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, that one, Sumire and Dr. Murad.\n\nApparently we made quite an impression by returning the 'Mech because Apple has contacted us through Yang and they are looking to hire us.",
