      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c1d11017f169562a31811ef"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Let us hope doing the right thing keeps working to our benefit.\n\nBut I do question why they have businesses in the Periphery border... [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMacintosh],Macintosh]] is a long way from here.",
