      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cbb0195de4d8ce167cb4870"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "You are the mercenaries who returned the pirated communications device to me.\n\nI am Duke Roberts of Macintosh, and the CEO of Apple Interstellar Computers.",
