    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c17ec2b7f9b662a1a7113e6"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Yes, because I chose so for a matter of secrecy because the matter at hand is too sensitive to be dealt by subordinates.\n\nHence you were summoned to this system.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "And why were we called here then?",
          "conditions": null,
