      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c379b5485748444c23a7e02"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "As a result, and with the personal support of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHanseDavion],First Prince]], I was ordered to develop a top secret project for the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreDavionAFFS],AFFS]].\n\nSince Macintosh has long been in the eye of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreISF],ISF]], [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMaskirovka],Maskirovka]] and [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSAFE],SAFE]], it was decided to set the research facility in an empty Periphery border world.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 14,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c145928ca3e905c360f4df8"
