    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd71f37c16224f2b10a4ea6"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "So a proper isolated planet was found in the system of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMavegh],Mavegh]]... where we thought that neither damn [[DM.Factions[faction_Kurita],Kurita]] or [[DM.Factions[faction_Liao],Liao]] eyes would ever found it.\n\nApparently we were wrong for several weeks ago our supply [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreJumpShip],JumpShip]] received a garbled and untranslatable transmission from the base.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 15,
