        "id": "9cd49d94b5143e469adbdcea"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "And what type of research is Apple conducting in a backwater [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeriphery],Periphery]] world?\n\nYou don't need to be a hermit to write software, your Grace.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
