        "id": "9c1b129c4bcb9964d641a19c"
      },
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Despite your past record with us, the fact that this command crew is made of a Capellan, Free Worlds Leaguer and even a <i>Kuritan</i> is enough for me to retain that knowledge from you for security reasons.\n\nFor all I know any of the other [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSuccessorState],houses]] can be behind this... and all of you might be on their payroll.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
